@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### Login as admin (to test admin-only delete)
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@gmail.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

