### ========================================
### NOTIFICATIONS API
### ========================================

### Create a notification (as admin, explicit userId)
# @name createNotification
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "userId": "e9025023-ea8e-4b42-9471-a03e9a650fea",
  "title": "Appointment Confirmed",
  "message": "Your appointment on 2024-05-01 at 10:00 AM has been confirmed.",
  "type": "APPOINTMENT"
}

###

### Create a notification (as patient, userId defaults to current user)
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

{
  "title": "Reminder",
  "message": "You have an upcoming appointment tomorrow.",
  "type": "REMINDER"
}

###

### Get all notifications (patient sees only their own)
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

### Get all notifications (admin can filter by userId)
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications?userId=e9025023-ea8e-4b42-9471-a03e9a650fea
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get notifications filtered by isRead=false (unread only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications?isRead=false
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

### Get notifications filtered by isRead=true (read only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications?isRead=true
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

### Get notifications with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

### Get notifications with all filters (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications?userId=9e0012cb-348b-44bd-b44e-102f117ec324&isRead=false&page=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get a single notification by ID
@notificationId = {{createNotification.response.body.id}}
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/{{notificationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

### Update notification — mark as read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/notifications/{{notificationId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}

{
  "isRead": true
}

###

### Update notification — change title and message
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/notifications/{{notificationId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "title": "Updated Title",
  "message": "Updated notification message.",
  "type": "SYSTEM"
}

###

### Delete a notification (admin only — expect 200)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/notifications/{{notificationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Delete a notification as non-admin (expect 403)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/notifications/{{notificationId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{patientToken}}
